<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>홍채 맵핑 자동화</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css?v=20260616-auth-main-2">
</head>
<body>
  <section id="authScreen" class="auth-screen">
    <div class="auth-card">
      <div class="auth-brand">
        <span class="auth-logo" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <strong>IRIS MAPPING LAB</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="auth-title">
        <h1>눈동자 상세 맵핑</h1>
        <p>홍채 분석을 통한 건강 인사이트</p>
      </div>

      <div class="auth-hero" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <p class="auth-quote">“눈동자는 마음의 창이자<br>신체의 지도를 담고 있습니다.”</p>

      <div class="auth-panel">
        <h2>로그인</h2>
        <p class="auth-copy">이름과 전화번호로 분석을 시작하세요.</p>

        <form id="loginForm" class="auth-form">
          <label>이름 <input id="loginName" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="이름" required></label>
          <label>전화번호 <input id="loginPhone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="전화번호" required></label>
          <button class="primary" type="submit">로그인</button>
        </form>

        <div class="auth-divider"><span>또는</span></div>

        <form id="signupForm" class="auth-form signup-form">
          <label>이름 <input id="signupName" type="text" autocomplete="name" placeholder="이름" required></label>
          <label>전화번호 <input id="signupPhone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="전화번호" required></label>
          <label>이메일 <input id="signupEmail" type="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="이메일"></label>
          <label>주소 <input id="signupAddress" type="text" autocomplete="street-address" placeholder="주소"></label>
          <label>추천인 <input id="signupReferrer" type="text" placeholder="추천인"></label>
          <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <p id="authMessage" class="auth-message" role="status"></p>

      <footer class="auth-footer">
        <strong>IRIS MAPPING LAB</strong>
        <span>본 서비스는 의료 진단을 대체하지 않으며, 전문가 상담과 함께 활용하시기 바랍니다.</span>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main id="appShell" class="app-shell" hidden>
    <section class="workspace">
      <header class="topbar">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Iris Mapping Lab</p>
          <h1>눈동자 상세 맵핑</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">

          <label class="file-button primary">
            <input id="pairInput" type="file" accept="image/*" multiple>
            좌우 사진 2장
          </label>
          <button id="exportButton" type="button" disabled>판독하기</button>
          <label class="file-button">
  <input id="chartInput" type="file" accept="image/*">
  기준 홍채
</label>

<button id="mappingButton" type="button">
  홍채 맵핑
</button>

          

                   <button id="logoutButton" type="button">로그아웃</button>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="canvas-wrap">
        <canvas id="irisCanvas" width="1280" height="360"></canvas>
        <div id="emptyState" class="empty-state">
          <strong>좌우 홍채 사진 2장을 올려주세요</strong>
          <span>지도처럼 색상 섹터를 얹고, 클릭한 위치의 세부 구역을 오른쪽에서 보여줍니다.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="side-panel">
      <section class="panel-block">
        <h2>홍채 사진</h2>

        <div class="reference-preview">
          <img id="chartPreview" alt="기준 홍채사진 보기">
          <span id="chartEmpty">기존 홍채사진 없음</span>
        </div>

        <div class="photo-grid">
          <button class="photo-card active" type="button" data-eye="right">
            <span class="photo-title">우안</span>
            <span id="rightPhotoName" class="photo-name">사진 없음</span>
          </button>

          <button class="photo-card" type="button" data-eye="left">
            <span class="photo-title">좌안</span>
            <span id="leftPhotoName" class="photo-name">사진 없음</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <button id="swapEyesButton" type="button" disabled>좌우 배정 바꾸기</button>
        <p class="hint">기본값은 첫 번째 사진=우안, 두 번째 사진=좌안입니다. 실제와 다르면 배정을 바꿔주세요.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="panel-block">
        <h2>보정</h2>

        <label class="control">중심 X
          <input id="centerX" type="range" min="0" max="640" value="320" disabled>
        </label>

        <label class="control">중심 Y
          <input id="centerY" type="range" min="0" max="360" value="180" disabled>
        </label>

        <label class="control">동공 반지름
          <input id="pupilRadius" type="range" min="10" max="140" value="54" disabled>
        </label>

        <label class="control">홍채 반지름
          <input id="irisRadius" type="range" min="40" max="180" value="118" disabled>
        </label>

        <div class="button-row">
          <button id="autoDetectButton" type="button" disabled>AI 종합분석</button>
          <button id="clearMarkersButton" type="button" disabled>마커 지우기</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel-block">
        <h2>홍채 판독</h2>
        <div id="selectionDetails" class="selection-details">
          <p>홍채의 선, 점, 색 변화 위치를 클릭하세요.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel-block">
        <h2>홍채 맵핑</h2>
        <div id="detailMap" class="detail-map"></div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel-block">
        <h2>AI 종합 분석</h2>
        <div id="markerList" class="marker-list empty">아직 기록된 위치가 없습니다.</div>
      </section>

      <p class="notice">참고용 맵핑 도구입니다. 의료 진단 또는 치료 판단 용도로 사용하지 마세요.</p>
    </aside>
  </main>
  <script src="iris-organ-db.js"></script>
  <script src="app.js?v=20260616-reading-page-restore-1"></script>
</body>
</html>
